article.headline: TCU 59, Air Force 56
article.story: FORT WORTH, Texas -- Hank Thorns scored 22 points and TCU held on to beat Air Force 59-56 on Wednesday night. J.R. Cadot added 13 points for TCU (12-7, 2-2 Mountain West). He was 7 for 7 from the free-throw line and also led the Horned Frogs in rebounds with seven. Taylor Broekhuis led the Falcons (11-7, 1-3) with 15 points and seven rebounds. Mike Fitzgerald scored 14 points and Todd Fletcher scored 12 for Air Force. Thorns' basket with 3:02 remaining represented the final points of the game. The Horned Frogs didn't attempt any free throws, but Air Force missed a 3-pointer at the buzzer. Air Force led 28-26 at the half behind Broekhuis' 11 points.
